\caption{\label{fig8} Real (a) and imaginary (b) parts of the wavevectors of the five lowest order modes of a $\mathcal{PT}$ symmetric waveguide for $N=1.5$. Real (c) and imaginary (d) parts of the wavevectors of the five lowest order modes of a $\mathcal{PT}$ symmetric waveguide for $N=2$.}
